            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName key="#Priests"><name>Anacardo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbitero</rs> rectori <rs key="#Churches"
                            >ecclesiae</rs> beati <orgName key="#Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/232">Sancti Petri</orgName> sita in loco
                            <placeName key="#Churches" ref="#places/597">Castellione</placeName>
                        prope <placeName>Fernetam</placeName>
                        <foreign>dona pro anima</foreign> Deo et tibi <rs key="#Churches"
                            >ecclesiae</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches #Private_foundations" ref="#juridical_persons/613"
                            >beati Sancti Colombani</orgName>, <rs key="#Private_foundations"
                            >constructa</rs> a viro beatissimo domno <persName
                            key="#Bishops #Private_foundations" ref="#people/343">Peredeo</persName>
                        in Dei nomine <rs key="#Bishops">episcopo</rs> prope <rs key="#Walls"
                            >murum</rs>
                        <rs key="#Cities">civitatis</rs> nostrae <placeName
                            key="#Cities #Walls #Churches #Private_foundations" ref="#places/4"
                            >Lucensis</placeName>, <rs key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs> ipsam ubi
                        resedere videor, cum <rs key="#Landed_possessions">omnibus rebus</rs> meis,
                        tam quam ipsam rem quam ibidem per dotem confirmavi quam et ubique mihi
                        pertenentem <rs key="#Cereals">terram</rs>, <rs key="#Wine">vineam</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Fruits/vegetables">orta</rs>, <rs key="#Oil">oliveta</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Acorns">silvas</rs>, <rs key="#Chestnuts">castaneum</rs>,
                        virgarium (…), nisi scerpham meam et pannos, buttes et arca vel alia
                        usitilia casae seu <rs key="#Animals">nutrimina</rs>, quae in meam reservo
                        potestatem. <foreign>Ne riserva l’usufrutto vitalizio, ma non la possibilità
                            di cedere i beni, per sé et per</foreign>
                        <persName><name>Auriperta</name></persName> presbiteria mea (…).
                            <foreign>Dopo la sua morte i beni e la chiesa appartengano</foreign> in
                        iamdicta ecclesia <foreign>(scil. di S. Colombano)</foreign> vel de <rs
                            key="#Bishops">pontefice</rs> qui pro tempore fuerit (…). Actum
                            <placeName ref="#places/4">Luca</placeName>.
                            <foreign>Sottoscrizioni:</foreign> (ss) Anacard presbiter; + <persName
                                key="#Witness #Specialized_workers"><name>Petti</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Specialized_workers">aurificis</rs> germani eius testis; +
                                <persName key="#Witness #Other_clerics"><name>Peretheuli</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">acoliti</rs> filii quondam
                                <persName><name>Gauderali</name></persName> testis; (ss)
                                <persName key="#Witness #Priests"><name>Firmo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiter</rs>; (ss)
                                <persName key="#Witness #Other_clerics"><name>Sprinca</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clericus</rs>; (ss)
                                <persName key="#Witness #Other_clerics"><name>Emmo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clericus</rs>. <foreign>Scrive</foreign>: <persName
                            key="#Writer #Other_clerics"><name>Austripertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clericus</rs>.</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
